data.description: Welcome to 320 W 9th St S, Newton, IA 50208. This charming home boasts original hardwood flooring throughout and a beautiful built-in wood-burning fireplace in the cozy living room. With two bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a versatile office with French doors, this home offers comfort and flexibility. The kitchen comes equipped with essential appliances, and a new roof in 2023 enhances its durability. A one-car attached garage and a wood-burning fireplace in the backyard complement the property. Notably, a park across the street adds to the neighborhood's appeal. Please be aware that this home is being sold as-is, with a non-functional dishwasher. The furnace was recently fixed.
